platformAttributes.ios.subtitle.k: Photos en direct des vos amis

platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.st.k: Lockets innovative pairing of widgets with real-time photo updates has made it a staple of our phones. Its helped us see small moments we mightve missed (like our baby cousin on a swing) and big moments we wish we hadnt missed (like our grown cousins graduation). Sometimes it was just reassurance our loved ones were on their way homeand that wed see them soon.
